Package: stmra
Type: Package
Title: Spatiotemporal Multiresolution Apprxomations for Gaussian Processes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Marius",
                 family = "Appel",
                 role = c("aut", "cre"),
                 email = "marius.appel@uni-muenster.de",
                 comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5281-3896")),
             person(given = "Matthias",
                 family = "Katzfuss",
                 role = "cph"))
Maintainer: Marius Appel <marius.appel@uni-muenster.de>
Description: Approximation of spatiotemporal Gaussian processes at multiple resolutions (see Katzfuss (2017) <doi:10.1080/01621459.2015.1123632>),
    where the domain of interest is recursively partitioned into smaller regions and regions
    at the same partitioning level are assumed to be conditionally independent. 
